snippet.title: Warner Bro's can't avoid the Amber Heard problem forever
snippet.description:
The last 4 years have been quite interesting for Actress Amber Heard. After she and Johnny Depp filed for divorce in 2016, her life has been a whirlwind of protection and lavish praise from the media. That same media has demonized Johnny Depp time and time again, and are now absolutely silent when Depp is fighting back against defamation claims and allegations put forward by Heard. Here I take a look at the history of the two characters, explain the media backlash and cover-up, and give my opinion about what I think will happen to Amber Heard, AQUAMAN 2, and potentially Jail.
